quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,"Walamma jaat rusulunaibraheema bilbushra qaloo innamuhlikoo ahli hathihi alqaryati inna ahlaha kanoothalimeen"
  29,32,"Qala inna feeha lootanqaloo nahnu aAAlamu biman feehalanunajjiyannahu waahlahu illa imraatahu kanat minaalghabireen"
  29,33,"Walamma an jaat rusulunalootan see-a bihim wadaqa bihim tharAAan waqaloola takhaf wala tahzan inna munajjookawaahlaka illa imraataka kanat mina alghabireen"
  29,34,"Inna munziloona AAala ahli hathihialqaryati rijzan mina assama-i bima kanooyafsuqoon"
  29,35,"Walaqad tarakna minha ayatanbayyinatan liqawmin yaAAqiloon"
  29,36,"Wa-ila madyana akhahumshuAAayban faqala ya qawmi oAAbudoo Allahawarjoo alyawma al-akhira wala taAAthaw feeal-ardi mufsideen"
  29,37,"Fakaththaboohu faakhathat-humuarrajfatu faasbahoo fee darihim jathimeen"
  29,38,"WaAAadan wathamooda waqad tabayyanalakum min masakinihim wazayyana lahumu ashshaytanuaAAmalahum fasaddahum AAani assabeeli wakanoomustabsireen"
